    <section class="docker-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y conceptos de Docker</li>
        <li>Imágenes, contenedores y Dockerfiles</li>
        <li>Ejemplos de uso y buenas prácticas</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="docker-quote">"Docker simplifica el desarrollo, despliegue y portabilidad de aplicaciones."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.docker-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.docker-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.docker-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #2496ed;
}
.docker-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #2496ed;
}
.docker-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.docker-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #2496ed;
}
.docker-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.docker-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.docker-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #e1f3ff;
  border-left: 4px solid #2496ed;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #176ba0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2496ed 0%, #4fc3f7 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #2496ed22;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4fc3f7 0%, #2496ed 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #2496ed44;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .docker-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .docker-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
